defaultQ148 default&#xa0; 
defaultPaul Blomfield:default We have discussed the issue of RAB charges before, Minister.  You will recall that, in those distant days when we were debating a new funding regime, your projection for the RAB charge was 28%.  That was subsequently revised upwards
default,
